procedureJavascriptCode.name: New Procedure Javascript Code
procedureJavascriptCode.code:
/* Loop Code */
// Highest Volume Index, by quantum8
let length = 10

let candle = record.current
let volume = getElement('volumes', candle)
let totalVol = volume.buy + volume.sell


let highest = 0
let hvi = 0


variable.volArr.push(totalVol)
if (variable.volArr.length > length) {
    variable.volArr.splice(0, 1)

    highest = Math.max(...variable.volArr)

    variable.highestPrev = variable.highestPrev == 0 ? totalVol : variable.highestPrev
    variable.highestPrev = isFinite(variable.highestPrev) ? variable.highestPrev : totalVol

    hvi = totalVol * 100 / variable.highestPrev
}

variable.highestPrev = highest  // save for next iteration

variable.value = hvi
